First Bank of Nigeria Limited is set to reward customers for Verve Card usage in its Free Fuel Promotion. The Free Fuel promo which was activated by FirstBank in collaboration with Verve International and Oando Plc, will run till Friday, 24 July 2020. In the promo, for a minimum of N3,000 fuel purchase, FirstBank Verve Cardholders will receive five extra litres of fuel free instantly at selected Oando Fuel Stations across Lagos every Monday, Tuesday and Thursday. Verve card is a secure debit card that allows the cardholder to conveniently meet day to day financial needs such as payment for goods and services, airtime recharge, bill payments, funds transfer, etc. It is accepted across all ATMs, POS, Web and Mobile Platforms in Nigeria. 